data.description: Rare opportunity to own a 3 Bed, 1.75 bath home in this area with over 5 acres! Walk inside & fall in love with this freshly updated home. Kitchen features solid wood cabinets, new counter & new appliances. Spacious floorplan is highlighted by 2 seperate living areas. One is open to the kitchen and features a woodburning stove. Updates include all NEW paint,millwork,doors,fixtures & flooring. Bathrooms have been completely updated with new tub surrounds & vanities. Walk outside onto your brand NEW deck & overlook the stunning view of the valley. Exterior features RV/Boat parking, multiple oversized storage buildings including a detached 2 car garage.Endless possibilities with Large attached greenhouse! Don’t miss out on this great property!
